OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FThe murder of Emma Caldwell was likely
OL,8,Fnot the first killing carried out by
OL,9,FIain Packer, the man convicted 19
OL,10,Fyears after her death, according to a
OL,11,Fformer detective.
OL,13,FRetired detective constable Stuart
OL,14,FHall, who was involved in the initial
OL,15,Finvestigation into the murder, has
OL,16,Ftold a podcast he believes "there's
OL,17,Fgoing to be more found out in the
OL,18,Ffuture" regarding Packer's offending.
OL,26,@xD@\OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
