OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776052540
OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FMs Caldwell, 27, was killed in 2005
OL,8,Fbut it was not until 2024 that Packer
OL,9,Fwas convicted of her murder, along
OL,10,Fwith a string of sexual offences
OL,11,Fagainst other women.
OL,13,FPolice had questioned Packer in the
OL,14,Fweeks after the death of Ms Caldwell,
OL,15,Fbut instead a group of Turkish men
OL,16,Fwere charged in relation to her death
OL,17,Fin 2007. The case against them later
OL,18,Fcollapsed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
