PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776052540
OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FMr Hall spoke to a podcast series
OL,8,Fwhich is examining the deaths of a
OL,9,Fnumber of women involved in
OL,10,Fprostitution around Glasgow in the
OL,11,F1990s and early 2000s.
OL,13,FThe Beware Book podcast examines the
OL,14,Fdeaths of eight women during the
OL,15,Fperiod, four of which remain unsolved.
OL,17,FThe Clyde 1 podcast takes its name
OL,18,Ffrom a journal which was used by women
OL,19,Finvolved in prostitution to warn each
OL,20,Fother about potentially dangerous or
OL,21,Fsuspicious clients.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
