SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776052540
OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FMr Hall was asked about the fact that
OL,8,FPacker's offending continued for years
OL,9,Fafter Ms Caldwell's murder, and
OL,10,Fwhether the full extent of his crimes
OL,11,Fhas come to light.
OL,13,FHe said: "No ` short answer. I think
OL,14,Fthere's a lot more to be found out
OL,15,Fabout Iain Packer.
OL,17,F"Personally, I don't think it was his
OL,18,Ffirst murder.
OL,26,@uD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776052540
OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,F"I think there's going to be more
OL,8,Ffound out in the future. I'd love to
OL,9,Fbe involved in something to do with
OL,10,Fthat, but I think there's far more to
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,F"There's a pattern of behaviour here.
OL,14,FAs they discovered during the trial,
OL,15,Fwhich is now common knowledge, he did
OL,16,Fthe same thing to several girls.
OL,18,F"Although Emma was the only one we
OL,19,Fknow of at this time who was murdered.
OL,20,FI see no reason for there not to be
OL,21,Fmore."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
