OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FMr Hall said Packer's history of
OL,8,Fviolence against women had emerged in
OL,9,Fcourt.
OL,11,FHe continued: "That just seems to be
OL,12,Fwho he is, how he deals with life and
OL,13,Fwomen."
OL,15,FPacker was jailed for life with a
OL,16,Fminimum term of 36 years after he was
OL,17,Ffound guilty of Ms Caldwell's murder.
OL,19,FHer body was found as a remote
OL,20,Flocation in Limefield Woods in South
OL,21,FLanarkshire.
OL,26,@sD@OOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
