OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FOther former detectives have
OL,8,Fpreviously told the podcast about
OL,9,Ftheir certainty of Packer's guilt.
OL,11,FHowever they said their suspicions
OL,12,Fwere dismissed by superiors, with one
OL,13,Fbeing told Packer "will never be
OL,14,Faccused".
OL,16,FA public inquiry, chaired by Lord
OL,17,FScott KC, is due to examine the police
OL,18,Finvestigation into the murder.
OL,26,@uD@SOUvD@HO]
