OL,3,CEmma Caldwell unlikely to have been
OL,4,Cher killer's first victim, says ex-
OL,5,Cdetective
OL,7,FPolice Scotland Deputy Chief Constable
OL,8,FAlan Speirs said: "Emma Caldwell's
OL,9,Ffamily have shown incredible courage
OL,10,Fand determination following her murder
OL,11,Fin 2005 and we are absolutely
OL,12,Fcommitted to supporting the inquiry
OL,13,Fand getting her loved ones the answers
OL,14,Fthey deserve."
OL,26,@pD@SOUvD@NO]
